des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Hammerton Smart Light. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our Hammerton Smart Light app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our Hammerton Smart Light app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search Hammerton Smart Light skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable Hammerton Smart Light skill, and you'll be navigated to the Hammerton Smart Light login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to warm white."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
